"Mary Katharine Cahill,

664
00:40:46,075 --> 00:40:48,407
"a daughter of Harriet M. Barr

665
00:40:48,511 --> 00:40:51,571
"and Archibald W. Barr
of Stonington, Connecticut,

666
00:40:51,681 --> 00:40:53,808
"and Kevin Mark Duncan III,

667
00:40:53,916 --> 00:40:55,907
"a son of Beatrice Hoslinger

668
00:40:56,018 --> 00:40:58,919
"and Kevin Mark Duncan, Jr.,
of Manhattan,

669
00:40:59,021 --> 00:41:00,488
"were married last evening

670
00:41:00,590 --> 00:41:02,854
at the Episcopal Church
of the Heavenly Rest. "

671
00:41:02,959 --> 00:41:04,358
He travels around the country

672
00:41:04,460 --> 00:41:06,894
and collects miniature
replicas of monuments...

673
00:41:06,996 --> 00:41:09,624
Washington Memorial,
Bunker Hill, Mount Rushmore...

674
00:41:09,732 --> 00:41:12,166
